name: Grand Efreet Brazier
category: Features
footprint: 2x2
facing: no
shadow: yes
blocks_light: no
height: 1.5
placement: center
room_types: elemental-fire-node, genie-court, volcano-caldera
typical_count: single
clusters_with: fire-node-core, flame-pillar, lava-fountain
notes: Huge ornate brazier with brass filigree and raging orange flames. Top-down shows the brass rim and central flame; efreeti silhouettes carved into the outer band.
lights: [{"preset":"brazier","x":1,"y":1,"radius":18,"intensity":1,"color":"#ff7030"}]
---
# Outer heat halo
circle 1.0,1.0 0.95 gradient-radial #ff6030 #1a0800 0.35

# Outer brass filigree band (ornate outer ring)
circle 1.0,1.0 0.85 texfill polyhaven/metal_plate 0.85
circle 1.0,1.0 0.85 fill #daa520 0.5
circle 1.0,1.0 0.85 stroke #5a3a00 width 3

# Filigree detail — eight radial arms
line 1.0,0.15 1.0,0.3 stroke #5a3a00 width 2
